snippet: Cink birdied seven of the final 11 holes for a seven-under-par 64 and a share of the first-round lead with Martin Laird in the Shriners Hospitals for Children Open in Las Vegas.
abstract: Stewart Cink and Martin Laird share first-round lead at the Shriners Hospitals for Children Open in Las Vegas; other golf news noted.
lead_paragraph: Cink birdied seven of the final 11 holes for a seven-under-par 64 and a share of the first-round lead with Martin Laird in the Shriners Hospitals for Children Open in Las Vegas.

headline.main: Stewart Cink Grabs Share of Lead
